Package junit

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JunitParent
    Interface implemented by the JunitRepresentation and JunitPackage, provides a method the get its JunitPackages
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JunitAssertion
    Represents an junit assertion which will be printed in the mustache template
    JunitConstructorUnderTest  
    JunitFieldUnderTest  
    JunitMethodUnderTest  
    JunitPackage
    A package containing one or more JunitTestClasses.
    JunitPackageTest
    Tests the functionalities of JunitPackage
    JunitParameterUnderTest
    Represents a parameter of a JunitConstructorUnderTest or JunitMethodUnderTest with its final modifier value.
    JunitRepresentation
    Represents the junit representation which is used to fill the mustache template
    JunitRepresentationTest
    Tests the functionalitites of JunitRepresentation
    JunitTemplateParameterUnderTest  
    JunitTestClass
    Represents a test class which will be converted in a mustache template
    TestInitializer
    Provides mock elements and an initialization method.
    Must be extended by all test classes of this package.
